title: Fire & Blood: The Ascension of Jaehaerys & Alysanne
description:
Edited audio from the livestream on New Year's Day 2019. Guests are Lady Gwyn of Radio Westeros and Chloe of Girls Gone Canon. We discuss Aegon the Uncrowned, succession issues, the rich Sansa/Alysanne parallels, the Targaryen family tree retcon, Jon's "real" name, and quite a bit more!
